data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
* popupMenu1 is reusing the parentBarItem2 (Edit menu) in the main-menu.
* popupMenu2 hosts a custom ParentBarItem (parentBarItem8). Use the "Add Default ParentBarItem" verb in the PopupMenu to create a new ParentBarItem.
* The popupMenusManager1 provides context menu functionality to Controls on your Form.
* This TextBox and the above Label are associated with these popups (as Context Menus) through the PopupMenusManager's XPContextMenu extended property.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
* Hover over barItems to see SuperToolTips instead of normal toolTips.
* The Client area is enclosed in a Panel with DockStyle.Fill to handle dynamic resisizing due to the toolbars docking to the different sides.
* The TextBox below has a PopupMenu associated with it.
* There is an XPToolBar docked to the Top of the Panel to the right.
